blurb.en-US:
flamingo

I love KeroKeroBonito. Her music feels like me, when I listen to it I get creative. So it made sense for me to make a music video for her song flamingo. It's the best way I can thank her!

[She even tweeted about it!](https://twitter.com/KeroKeroBonito/status/734700356706394112)

I'm always drawing and animating for fun, and I freelance! I like to tell stories through info graphics and love learning new concepts. 

Drop me a line and lets tell stories!

🙋I'm Charlie!

This my official website. I'm very official!

I may look like a librarian, but I check out more than books!

I secretly draw my drawings in a small Muji notebook, then craft my animations on my compact 2012 macbook air. If they aren't *too* raunchy or *too* silly, I'll share them here and on instagram. 

If I haven't posted in a while, it's because my mind is in the gutter and I'm drawing dicks all the time.

Bell.studio made the webiste, thanks Phil!
